ComicInfo.Summary:
Barney Don't Surf: Tank Girl and crew are chased by bounty hunters, and end up in 1960s California, where they meet the Kook Patrol.
Turn Up, Drop In, Wipe Out: Introducing the Kook Patrol, a group of surfers from 1960s California.
Shoes 50% Off: The Tank Girl crew have fun at David's Soles, a shoe store.
Rangers of the Universe, Part One: Tank Girl and crew go on a quest to Booga's childhood holiday cottage to dig up a vintage action figure.
